1
00:00:15,416 --> 00:00:16,667
Boyfriend mo ba siya?

2
00:00:16,938 --> 00:00:17,897
Hindi...

3
00:00:17,922 --> 00:00:18,965
Hindi niya boyfriend.

4
00:00:18,990 --> 00:00:20,158
Classmate ko siya.

5
00:00:20,183 --> 00:00:22,143
Walang iba ang na-hack ng account ni Freya ng...

6
00:00:22,168 --> 00:00:24,462
Edrix Knight.

7
00:00:24,636 --> 00:00:25,762
May utang ka na naman sa akin.

8
00:00:25,851 --> 00:00:26,977
Magpasalamat ka kay Keifer.

9
00:00:27,282 --> 00:00:29,242
- Huwag masyadong madamot.
- Isa lang salamat.

10
00:00:29,267 --> 00:00:31,815
Teka! Napakaingay niyo lahat!
Bakit mo ako pinipilit?

11
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:34,301
Simula ngayon, walang kakain sa itaas.

12
00:00:34,559 --> 00:00:36,686
Uhh, Jay... hindi ba tayo magtatanong
kasama natin silang kumain?

13
00:00:37,104 --> 00:00:39,273
Bakit hindi natin sila ipagluto?

14
00:00:39,467 --> 00:00:40,928
Mayroon kaming ilang mga kagamitan sa kusina dito, tama ba?

15
00:00:40,952 --> 00:00:41,786
Huwag hawakan ang mga iyon.

16
00:00:41,811 --> 00:00:43,188
- Sino ang nagmamay-ari sa kanila?
- Eman.

17
00:00:43,918 --> 00:00:46,254
Tutulungan kami hanggang
gumaling ang iyong restaurant.

18
00:00:46,285 --> 00:00:47,495
At sino ang "tayo"

19
00:00:49,090 --> 00:00:50,215
Anong meron sa kanya?

20
00:00:50,216 --> 00:00:51,718
<i>[nagsisigawan ang mga customer]</i>

21
00:00:51,743 --> 00:00:53,328
Kahit papaano nagbago ang ihip ng hangin, ha?

22
00:00:53,986 --> 00:00:54,986
anong ginagawa mo

23
00:00:55,180 --> 00:00:57,265
<i>[nagsisigawan ang mga customer]</i>

24
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:00,648
Maaari ba kitang hawakan ng isang beses?

25
00:01:00,966 --> 00:01:02,593
Gusto mo itong maramdaman?

26
00:01:02,996 --> 00:01:04,039
Gusto mo bang maramdaman ito?

27
00:01:06,266 --> 00:01:07,518
Alam mo naman na ikaw ang may kasalanan diba?

28
00:01:07,542 --> 00:01:09,225
Oo, tama. nagpapagamot ako
sugat mo ngayon ha?

29
00:01:09,249 --> 00:01:10,751
Bakit kailangan mo laging makialam?

30
00:01:10,776 --> 00:01:13,612
Hindi ako matahimik
kapag alam kong pwedeng magbago ang mga bagay.

31
00:01:13,834 --> 00:01:15,086
Hindi pwedeng wala lang ako.

32
00:01:19,829 --> 00:01:21,414
Halika na!

33
00:01:21,439 --> 00:01:22,815
Tatayo ka ba dito buong araw?

34
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,840
sus.

35
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:43,477
Isa lang ang isusuot mo?

36
00:01:43,478 --> 00:01:45,358
- Magsuot ka pareho, siyempre.
- Order para sa Talahanayan 3.

37
00:01:48,983 --> 00:01:50,109
pasensya na po.

38
00:01:51,179 --> 00:01:51,888
Bakit?

39
00:01:51,972 --> 00:01:53,015
Ano bang problema mo?

40
00:01:53,515 --> 00:01:55,267
Paano nalaman ni Aries na nandito kami?

41
00:01:55,601 --> 00:01:56,601
Aries?

42
00:01:57,269 --> 00:01:58,729
Magdudulot din ba sila ng gulo dito?

43
00:01:59,104 --> 00:02:00,689
OMG!

44
00:02:01,148 --> 00:02:02,232
Kaya totoo.

45
00:02:02,566 --> 00:02:04,735
Waitress ka lang ngayon.

46
00:02:05,277 --> 00:02:06,153
Waitress.

47
00:02:06,236 --> 00:02:07,529
Ito ay isang kagalang-galang na trabaho.

48
00:02:10,073 --> 00:02:11,450
Keifer Watson?

49
00:02:11,992 --> 00:02:12,992
What the hell?

50
00:02:13,452 --> 00:02:14,452
Seryoso,

51
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,120
naghihirap ka na ba?

52
00:02:18,290 --> 00:02:19,291
hindi ko alam.

53
00:02:19,333 --> 00:02:20,500
Bakit hindi mo tanungin ang kaibigan ko?

54
00:02:25,964 --> 00:02:26,964
Babae!

55
00:02:27,007 --> 00:02:28,508
Nandito ka rin pala Mica?

56
00:02:28,675 --> 00:02:32,011
Ay, hindi. Wala siya dito.
Isang picture lang.

57
00:02:32,012 --> 00:02:33,262
Minsan, hologram siya.

58
00:02:33,263 --> 00:02:34,348
Sobrang nakakatawa.

59
00:02:35,349 --> 00:02:37,726
Ahm, Jay. Kukunin ko ang mga order nila.

60
00:02:38,185 --> 00:02:39,185
Hindi.

61
00:02:40,187 --> 00:02:42,397
Gusto naming pagsilbihan kami nina Jay-jay at Keifer.

62
00:02:49,988 --> 00:02:50,988
Okay.

63
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,200
Uhm.

64
00:02:54,701 --> 00:02:55,701
Dito.

65
00:02:57,621 --> 00:02:58,455
Sige na.

66
00:02:58,580 --> 00:02:59,623
Ano ang problema sa kanila?

67
00:03:00,290 --> 00:03:01,290
Salamat, Jay.

68
00:03:03,335 --> 00:03:04,335
Menu.

69
00:03:04,961 --> 00:03:06,171
Shoo! Shoo! Shoo!

70
00:03:15,514 --> 00:03:16,515
Wag kang gumalaw.

71
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:25,691
<i>Bakit niya ako niyakap ulit?
Umorder ka lang, please!</i>

72
00:03:26,149 --> 00:03:26,983
babalik na lang ako!

73
00:03:27,109 --> 00:03:28,819
Hoy, Yuri! Kalmado ka ba?

74
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:32,239
Hayaan mo na lang sila Keifer.

75
00:03:32,781 --> 00:03:36,535
Hindi siya magdudulot ng eksena
para guluhin ang negosyo ni Eman.

76
00:03:36,993 --> 00:03:37,993
Okay?

77
00:03:40,288 --> 00:03:41,665
Kamusta na kaya sila diyan?

78
00:03:45,210 --> 00:03:46,210
<i>[Kiko clears his throat]</i>

79
00:03:46,420 --> 00:03:47,462
Pwede na ba tayong umorder?

80
00:03:49,381 --> 00:03:51,550
Kukuha ako ng Ultimate Pizza.

81
00:03:52,426 --> 00:03:53,426
Okay.

82
00:03:53,593 --> 00:03:55,762
magkakaroon ako ng pareho,
plus bottomless iced tea.

83
00:03:57,431 --> 00:04:01,267
Kukuha ako ng Goddess Salad,
ngunit hawakan ang alfalfa sprouts.

84
00:04:01,268 --> 00:04:05,689
At siguraduhin mong bibigyan kita
anim na cherry tomatoes. Wala na, walang kulang.

85
00:04:05,856 --> 00:04:08,984
At ang dressing, sa gilid. Obvious naman.

86
00:04:09,776 --> 00:04:11,153
Ikaw, Aries?

87
00:04:20,036 --> 00:04:21,496
Kukuha ako ng mozzarella sticks.

88
00:04:21,663 --> 00:04:22,873
Magdagdag pa ng sili dito.

89
00:04:23,123 --> 00:04:25,542
At sabihin sa chef na lutuin ito ng maayos.

90
00:04:25,667 --> 00:04:28,628
Gusto ko itong malambot sa loob.
At malutong sa labas.

91
00:04:28,712 --> 00:04:30,005
At siguraduhing hindi ito tuyo.

92
00:04:30,172 --> 00:04:30,672
Okay?

93
00:04:30,881 --> 00:04:31,881
Uhm.

94
00:04:31,923 --> 00:04:35,343
Kukuha ako ng sparkling water.
May kalang kalamansi sa gilid.

95
00:04:35,761 --> 00:04:36,803
Meron ba kayo niyan?

96
00:04:37,763 --> 00:04:38,388
Mm-hmm.

97
00:04:38,555 --> 00:04:40,315
Sigurado ka bang iyon lang
mayroon ka, babe?

98
00:04:40,724 --> 00:04:43,018
Order na lang ulit ako kung gusto ko.

99
00:04:43,894 --> 00:04:44,894
Yun lang muna.

100
00:04:47,397 --> 00:04:49,524
Teka. Nakuha mo ba ang lahat?

101
00:04:49,941 --> 00:04:50,941
Oo.

102
00:04:51,443 --> 00:04:52,569
Isinulat ko ito.

103
00:04:52,652 --> 00:04:53,779
Ulitin mo.

104
00:04:56,615 --> 00:04:57,615
Sige.

105
00:04:58,825 --> 00:05:01,786
Dalawang order ng Ultimate Pizza,
isang bottomless iced tea.

106
00:05:01,787 --> 00:05:04,205
Isang order ng Goddess Salad,
walang alfalfa sprouts.

107
00:05:04,206 --> 00:05:07,209
May anim na cherry tomatoes
at nagbibihis sa gilid.

108
00:05:07,417 --> 00:05:09,752
Isang order ng mozzarella
sticks, may dagdag na sili.

109
00:05:09,753 --> 00:05:10,545
Lutuin ito ng maayos.

110
00:05:10,546 --> 00:05:13,089
Malambot pero malutong pa rin. Hindi tuyo.

111
00:05:13,423 --> 00:05:15,217
At isang sparkling na tubig na may kalamansi.

112
00:05:15,300 --> 00:05:16,009
yun ba?

113
00:05:16,134 --> 00:05:18,010
Okay, salamat. magiging ako
pagkuha ng menu pagkatapos.

114
00:05:18,011 --> 00:05:19,429
Hindi, hayaan mo na.

115
00:05:19,763 --> 00:05:23,517
Sabi ng girlfriend ko oorder daw siya mamaya.

116
00:05:25,227 --> 00:05:28,104
Pagkatapos ay mag-iiwan ako ng isa sa iyong mesa. Okay?

117
00:05:29,689 --> 00:05:30,689
Sige.

118
00:05:31,566 --> 00:05:32,943
Halika na. Tara na.

119
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:37,364
<i>[Nagvibrate ang telepono]</i>

120
00:05:40,075 --> 00:05:41,743
Hey. Si Ram na naman ba yun?

121
00:05:42,452 --> 00:05:43,829
Huwag pansinin ang kanyang mga pagbabanta.

122
00:05:47,165 --> 00:05:48,749
Keifer, ibigay mo ito sa kusina.

123
00:05:48,750 --> 00:05:50,043
Aayusin ko lahat dito. Pumunta ka.

124
00:05:51,086 --> 00:05:52,086
Sige na.

125
00:05:57,884 --> 00:06:01,096
<i>[hindi malinaw na daldalan]</i>

126
00:06:01,972 --> 00:06:03,347
Keif, anong meron?

127
00:06:03,348 --> 00:06:04,348
Anong sabi ni Aries?

128
00:06:04,391 --> 00:06:05,391
As usual.

129
00:06:05,767 --> 00:06:06,893
Nandito sila para insultuhin tayo.

130
00:06:07,394 --> 00:06:09,521
Pero Keif... napansin mo rin naman diba?

131
00:06:10,230 --> 00:06:11,230
ano?

132
00:06:11,648 --> 00:06:14,276
Yung Jay-jay at Aries
ay hindi nasa mabuting kalagayan.

133
00:06:16,403 --> 00:06:18,737
Iniisip ko lang,
kung gusto mong bumalik kay Aries,

134
00:06:18,738 --> 00:06:20,218
saka bakit Jay-jay pa ang ginagamit mo?

135
00:06:22,367 --> 00:06:23,785
Hindi rin sila okay.

136
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:54,459
Jay, pwede ba kitang makausap?

137
00:07:55,585 --> 00:07:57,629
Pwede ba dito? May trabaho ako.

138
00:07:58,797 --> 00:08:00,340
Ako... Okay. Umm...

139
00:08:01,758 --> 00:08:02,842
Ay, Jay.

140
00:08:03,969 --> 00:08:05,303
Gusto kitang ligawan.

141
00:08:07,973 --> 00:08:09,390
Hindi ko pa nasasabi kay Aries,

142
00:08:09,391 --> 00:08:12,143
gusto ko lang marinig muna ang sagot mo.

143
00:08:12,268 --> 00:08:13,311
Uhm...

144
00:08:17,899 --> 00:08:19,901
Kiko, alam mo...

145
00:08:20,235 --> 00:08:21,736
Okay na ba ang lahat, Jay?

146
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,240
Oo.

147
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:27,784
Nag-uusap lang kami.

148
00:08:29,119 --> 00:08:30,578
- Umalis ka na.
- Ay, David...

149
00:08:30,829 --> 00:08:32,330
Baka kailangan ka sa loob?

150
00:08:32,998 --> 00:08:33,998
Ikaw din, Jay.

151
00:08:34,165 --> 00:08:35,325
Kailangan ka sa kusina.

152
00:08:35,917 --> 00:08:36,917
Tapos tayo na.

153
00:08:39,045 --> 00:08:40,045
Halika na.

154
00:08:44,050 --> 00:08:45,050
Jay.

155
00:08:45,802 --> 00:08:47,220
Hihintayin ko ang sagot mo.

156
00:08:48,013 --> 00:08:49,013
Oo naman.

157
00:08:51,474 --> 00:08:53,351
Oh... interesante.

158
00:08:54,060 --> 00:08:55,060
Kuya,

159
00:08:55,228 --> 00:08:56,229
Ano iyon?

160
00:08:56,646 --> 00:08:57,981
wala. Huwag kang mag-alala tungkol dito.

161
00:09:06,031 --> 00:09:07,031
Anong nangyari sayo?

162
00:09:13,705 --> 00:09:15,415
Bakit bigla kang liligawan ni Kiko?!

163
00:09:16,249 --> 00:09:17,375
Paano ko malalaman?

164
00:09:18,293 --> 00:09:19,461
At hinahayaan mo siya?

165
00:09:22,672 --> 00:09:23,672
Hindi.

166
00:09:24,090 --> 00:09:25,175
Gusto mo ba si Kiko?

167
00:09:26,593 --> 00:09:27,260
Ang bagay ay...

168
00:09:27,260 --> 00:09:28,260
Gusto mo siya.

169
00:09:30,889 --> 00:09:31,723
Hindi.

170
00:09:31,890 --> 00:09:33,810
At wala akong balak
hinahayaan din niya akong ligawan.

171
00:09:41,441 --> 00:09:44,611
Kailangan nating makasigurado
na ang kanyang plano ay hindi magtatagumpay.

172
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:48,531
Ngayon, bumalik tayo sa trabaho.

173
00:09:50,575 --> 00:09:51,575
Halika na.

174
00:09:53,953 --> 00:09:54,953
Keif.

175
00:09:55,663 --> 00:09:58,208
Ayaw mo kay Kiko
planong magtagumpay dahil...

176
00:09:59,125 --> 00:10:00,794
hadlang siya sa plano mo o...

177
00:10:01,544 --> 00:10:03,064
dahil concern ka kay Jay-jay?

178
00:10:05,131 --> 00:10:06,674
Ano pa ba ang tanong na iyon?

179
00:10:18,895 --> 00:10:19,895
<i>[Bumuntong hininga si Ci-N]</i>

180
00:10:20,772 --> 00:10:22,440
Nakakapagod talaga ito.

181
00:10:23,149 --> 00:10:24,150
may tanong ako.

182
00:10:24,442 --> 00:10:25,442
Hmm?

183
00:10:25,819 --> 00:10:27,654
Ano ang nangyari sa pagitan nina David at Kiko?

184
00:10:28,905 --> 00:10:30,299
Oh, pinag-uusapan mo ba ang laban nila?

185
00:10:30,323 --> 00:10:31,323
Oo.

186
00:10:31,866 --> 00:10:32,866
Okay.

187
00:10:32,909 --> 00:10:34,369
Sa pagkakaalam ko...

188
00:10:34,953 --> 00:10:36,662
Inireklamo ng Section A si Kit at Eren.

189
00:10:36,663 --> 00:10:38,498
- At pagkatapos?
- At pagkatapos, nakipag-usap sila kay David.

190
00:10:39,416 --> 00:10:41,251
Hindi ko alam ang mga detalye
ng kanilang talakayan.

191
00:10:42,252 --> 00:10:45,505
Pero narinig lang namin yun
nag-away sila sa lumang pabrika.

192
00:10:46,047 --> 00:10:48,675
Pagdating namin doon,
Dumudugo na ang mukha ni David.

193
00:10:48,758 --> 00:10:49,175
Oh?

194
00:10:49,176 --> 00:10:50,635
At may hawak na tubo si Kiko.

195
00:10:52,428 --> 00:10:54,347
Ginamitan ni Kiko ng tubo si David?

196
00:10:55,014 --> 00:10:56,224
Si Kiko talaga ang gumawa nun?

197
00:10:56,516 --> 00:10:57,516
Oo.

198
00:10:57,851 --> 00:10:59,651
Marami kang hindi
alam ni Kiko, Jay.

199
00:11:00,270 --> 00:11:02,355
Pero anong ginawa niyo?
Tinulungan mo ba si David?

200
00:11:03,648 --> 00:11:05,692
Si David ang orihinal na pangulo noon.

201
00:11:05,859 --> 00:11:07,193
- Oo.
- Ang kanyang panuntunan ay...

202
00:11:07,485 --> 00:11:09,612
dapat lumayo tayo
mula sa gulo hangga't kaya natin.

203
00:11:09,988 --> 00:11:13,241
Hindi iyon nagustuhan ng iba naming kaklase.
Tinawag nilang duwag si David. Mahina.

204
00:11:13,450 --> 00:11:15,827
Kaya, nang si Keifer ay naging presidente,
naging masaya sila.

205
00:11:16,035 --> 00:11:18,316
Hindi kasi kami papayagan ni Keifer
madaling matukso.

206
00:11:18,705 --> 00:11:19,914
Ipinaglalaban niya tayo.

207
00:11:20,832 --> 00:11:21,832
Sa totoo lang...

208
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:25,294
Parang tipong si Keifer
upang gamitin ang kanyang mga kamao upang makuha ang kanyang paraan.

209
00:11:25,295 --> 00:11:26,921
Lalo na sa mga kaibigan niya.

210
00:11:27,589 --> 00:11:28,590
sinabi mo.

211
00:11:29,340 --> 00:11:31,551
Pero si Kiko? Isang manggugulo?

212
00:11:33,344 --> 00:11:35,889
Tinamaan ka ng kanyang Amerikano
impit at matatamis na ngiti.

213
00:11:36,139 --> 00:11:37,139
hindi totoo yan.

214
00:11:37,182 --> 00:11:38,367
Hindi mo gusto ang mga lalaking nagsasalita ng Ingles?

215
00:11:38,391 --> 00:11:39,142
Hindi.

216
00:11:39,184 --> 00:11:40,184
Paano si Keifer?

217
00:11:40,810 --> 00:11:41,769
<i>[Panunukso ni Ci-N kay Jay-jay]</i>

218
00:11:41,770 --> 00:11:44,272
Titigilan mo ba yan?!
Magnanakaw ako ng sandwich mo.

219
00:11:45,565 --> 00:11:46,565
Keifer.

220
00:11:46,608 --> 00:11:47,608
Keifer.

221
00:11:48,109 --> 00:11:49,152
<i>[Ci-N tumatawa]</i>

222
00:11:57,243 --> 00:11:59,287
<i>[Hikab ni Jay-jay]</i>

223
00:12:00,163 --> 00:12:01,206
salamat po.

224
00:12:04,375 --> 00:12:06,044
Nakakainis yang mga Section A na yan.

225
00:12:06,544 --> 00:12:07,544
ayos ka lang?

226
00:12:08,838 --> 00:12:10,340
Salamat sa paghatid sa akin pauwi, Yuri.

227
00:12:10,673 --> 00:12:11,382
Walang problema.

228
00:12:11,383 --> 00:12:13,092
Halos hindi ka makalakad kanina..

229
00:12:14,761 --> 00:12:16,137
Oo. Salamat ulit.

230
00:12:16,346 --> 00:12:17,388
Magandang gabi...

231
00:12:19,515 --> 00:12:21,226
Ay, umaga na ngayon. 2 AM na.

232
00:12:22,101 --> 00:12:23,102
Magandang umaga din.

233
00:12:23,811 --> 00:12:26,022
Basta wag mong kakalimutan yung meeting mamaya.

234
00:12:26,231 --> 00:12:27,565
May ipapaalam si Eman.

235
00:12:28,191 --> 00:12:29,191
Okay.

236
00:12:29,192 --> 00:12:30,485
- Okay.
- Mag-ingat ka.

237
00:12:30,693 --> 00:12:32,195
Salamat ulit.

238
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:34,239
- Magandang gabi.
- Magandang gabi.

239
00:12:38,368 --> 00:12:39,744
<i>[Hikab ni Jay-jay]</i>

240
00:12:43,623 --> 00:12:44,916
Bye!

241
00:12:52,173 --> 00:12:53,173
<i>[Sumisigaw si Jay-jay]</i>

242
00:12:53,883 --> 00:12:54,883
